@misc{Goold2016The-role,
	abstract = {This topical review article gives an overview of the
		  interplay between quantum information theory and
		  thermodynamics of quantum systems. We focus on several
		  trending topics including the foundations of statistical
		  mechanics, resource theories, entanglement in thermodynamic
		  settings, fluctuation theorems and thermal machines. This
		  is not a comprehensive review of the diverse field of
		  quantum thermodynamics; rather, it is a convenient entry
